\fs18 \cf4 \cb31 \strokec4 She has never before received praise from so many strangers.\cb1 \
\cb31 "Those gentle songs gave me strength."\cb1 \
\cb31 "Finding music I could resonate with at my saddest moment was so moving..."\cb1 \
\cb31 "This style of music is so cute!!"\cb1 \
\cb31 The girl stares nervously at the screen. The small red dot marking new messages quivers along with her heartbeat, as she opens the same window over and over again\'97\cb1 \
\cb31 Just a little more... just a few more people seeing my music... a few more people seeing me, someone who's good for nothing but writing music...\cb1 \
\cb31 All I want is for a few more people to take power from this.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

