\fs18 \cf4 \cb31 \strokec4 From being dragged out the door by Nangong to signing her name on that contract... to the girl, the entire day passed as swiftly as a flash of summer lightning cutting through a rainy night.\cb1 \
\cb31 Like a dream, like playing house... in the end, it all belonged to the realm of "delusion."\cb1 \
\cb31 The moment they walked out, they were no longer three separate individuals, but a group: the Angels of Delusion. And the moment she walked out, she stopped being only Sunna, the songwriter working behind the scenes, and became an idol standing before her fans, expressing herself onstage.\cb1 \
\cb31 \'97This overwhelming delusion descending upon her was the most incredible gift she had ever known.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

