\fs18 \cf4 \cb31 \strokec4 "Why did you choose to step onto the stage?"\cb1 \
\cb31 Was it for the fans? For the glory under the spotlight? Or for that version of yourself who stayed in the corner, watching others play, too afraid to step forward?\cb1 \
\cb31 Maybe it was all of those. Or maybe it was none of them.\cb1 \
\cb31 All the girl knew was that the moment she gripped the microphone, her heartbeat would slow, and the world around her would fall quiet... until the drums kicked in, and the music rippled across the stage. In that split second, music's gentle light illuminated the time they all shared together.\cb1 \
\cb31 It felt as if they were angels, with wings capable of carrying everyone away from "the here and now."\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

